This was CIA  humor. There was nothing to crack. Just a holiday sweater left on Jonahs desk chair as a gift. Simple yet... far from it.

A Fresno Foxes hoodie like the one his father bought him the first time he took Jonah to a baseball game.
Jonah never forgot the look of joy on his father's face when the local team won; it was one of the happiest days of his childhood.
Twitchy Jonah is twitching.
